{"tid":2147873,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【愛犬跟場？】Twice開網上收費騷 負傷定延坐着唱","createTime":"2020-08-09T14:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T16:56:37.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"319711acf0d53fdc6f98ba407d7e2c47b519e4d2","tid":2147873,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20200809/s00009/37f23c9abfc22a122d9d2739ac5ee492.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20200809%2Fs00009%2F37f23c9abfc22a122d9d2739ac5ee492.jpg&h=526c14ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國人氣女團Twice今日透過應用程式V Live舉行網上收費演唱會。受傷成員定延今日負傷演出，獲安排全程坐在舞台旁邊獻唱，她表示看着隊友演出也很開心，自言傷勢已好轉，希望盡快康復表演給粉絲看。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwice於90分鐘的演唱會，換上多個不同造型，獻唱多首歌曲，包括《Fancy You》、《Stuck in my head》等，並透過視像與200多名粉絲互動。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Twice成員今早前往演唱會場地時，成員Momo抱着愛犬現身，粉絲大讚場面溫馨。<br />\n<br />\n（即時娛樂）"},{"pid":"e961c2e5f120c6e7382f75cbbacca471918309fb","tid":2147873,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4oZz40f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4oZz40f.gif&h=fb4059b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tVpRIP1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtVpRIP1.gif&h=f47b61dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝大家gchi<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0bb2f639953b1b1d484ebd6b5d2f7b5fdac1c5","tid":2147873,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:03:53.000Z","msg":"印狗辛苦了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26eb17f25c14803a5587e89bfe2c93417bef75c4","tid":2147873,"uid":320204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:05:34.000Z","msg":"藍毛毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/